1.5.2 Patch Update Request - Parameters
Parameter Type Description
field(s) to be
updated
String Any field that needs to be updated for e.g.
customerName, expiry_date,
registered_mobile etc.
attribs Array To be used to update / delete / add an
attrib parameter and value
attribs.op String Operation - “add” for adding a new attrib,
“remove” for deleting the attrib; “replace”
for changing the value of existing attrib
attribs.path String Path of attrib that needs to be added /
removed / updated
attribs.value String Value that needs to be added or updated in
case of add & replace respectively. Won’t
be required for remove operation
