1.10.4 Keystroke Dynamics Response - Parameters
Parameter Type Description
Score Integer Score computed based on the keystroke
metrics computed
Details Array Array of all metrics computed based
on the typing speed which determines
the score
j. Annexure 3 - Consent (Device) APIs
1.11 Register Device API
Register Device API is used to inform the Drona Pay system of the
unique device ID and its mapping to device parameters. The choice
of which parameter (IMEI, IMSI, SIM Identification number,
Advertisement ID, Firebase ID etc.) or combination is used to
uniquely identify Device ID is left to the Mobile App. This API is
called at time of installation of the App or at time of
On-boarding of users on the App.
[POST /device/register] to register a device
[DELETE /device/register/{deviceId}] to soft-delete a registered device.
[GET /device/{deviceId}] to fetch details of a registered device
1.11.1 Register Device API – Example
endpoint: /device/register
method: POST
header:"Content-Type: application/json"
body:
{
"deviceId": "d001",
"mobilenum": "+91.99999.99999",
"imei1": "AA-BBBBBB-CCCCCC-D",
"imei2": "AA-BBBBBB-CCCCCC-D",
"adid": "38400000-8cf0-11bd-b23e-10b96e40000d",
"accountid": "",
"fid": "",
"imsi": "",
"attribs": {
"make": "SAMSUNG",
"model": "SM-G925P",
"manufactureddate": "2021-10-05T07:57:13.500+05:30",
"version": {
"os_version": "11.2.3",
"date": "2021-10-05T07:57:13.500+05:30",
}
},
}
