This tab on the Menu comprises dashboards (real-time as well as
historic) for investigative analysis. The sub options include
● Transaction DB
● Party Dashboard
● Transaction Profile
● Data Analyzer
Post logging on to the platform we are directed to the Transaction
dashboard by default within the Analytics menu,details of which
are mentioned.
2.1 Transaction DB
The dashboard gets updated real time with key transaction
information and risk score for every transaction that is passed to
Drona Pay for evaluation along with decision details of evaluated
rules and failed rules. On clicking any particular transaction
entry, one can find the details of the decision including rules
evaluated and the rule(s) that failed for the transaction.
2.1.1 Transactions Filter
The filters can be used to view specific information as per
the user’s requirement, with filter options on Class (Txn
Identifier) and Score ( >= X, where X is between 0 to 100)
2.1.2 Parameters for Transaction DB
Details on the key parameters (Columns)of the table include
5 |','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "User Manual", "Page ID": 5, "Version": 1, "iTenantID": 17}');
