in the system as a payer/Payee.
● TxnScore Count_P30_Payee/TxnScore Count_P30_Payer:
Transaction Count for different scores as Payee/Payer
for the last 30 days.
● Relationships_P30_Payer/Relationships_P30_Payee:
Relationship with payees/Payers as Payer/Payee.
2.5 Dashboard : Additional features
All Drona Pay dashboards have a set of common additional features
that make them configurable, self-serve and easy to use. Listed
below are the key features that make it user-friendly and
valuable.
2.5.1 Personalization- selection, sequencing,addition
Clicking on the downward facing arrow right next to the main
menu , allows the user to make custom datagrid selections.
The user can add additional derived columns to the dashboard
table and also select columns by clicking on the checkbox in
front of each of the column names.Additionally, the user can
resequence the columns by dragging them.The applied selection
can be saved for all users/for currently logged in user.
