1.14.4 Device Profile Query API – Parameters
Parameter Type Description
progress {} shows progress of processing device log
of this deviceId.
sms_profile Profile generated from sms log
sms_profile.overall Overall summary statistics computed from
sms log data
sms_profile.per_bank [] Per bank statistics computed from sms
log data
sms_profile.per_card [] Per card statistics computed from sms
log data
sms_profile.per_loan [] Statistics computed per loan from sms
log data
sms_profile.per_utility [] Statistics computed per utility from sms
log data
geo_profile [] Profile generated from device location
and statistics computed based on the
location log data
1.15 User Profile (Email & Mobile) Query API
1.15.1 User Profile Request Parameters
User Profile Query API is used to validate a user''s email address
& mobile number. The client system can query a user’s profile
based on name, email address and mobile number to validate all
three parameters and the likelihood that they are fraudulent.
endpoint: /api/v1/user/info
method: POST
