the App on the Device. The Device Info is categorized into
following categories and each of the categories may be sent
separately or jointly:
Contacts
Call Log
SMS Log
Emails
Apps
Location
Device Info can be submitted in two ways:
1. Submit as a regular POST call
2. Upload a compressed file containing json objects
Example JSON input message structure for Device Info is given
below:
1.13.1 Device Info API – Example
endpoint: /device/info/{deviceId}
method: POST
header:"Content-Type: application/json"
