lity of the JSON logic, making it easier to understand and maintain. ● All functional checks in one IF block: o Move all functional checks into one separate IF block. This consolidation of functional checks simplifies the logic and ensures that all the relevant checks are grouped together for better clarity and coherence. Process to Configure,Unit Test and Deploy Rules ● The process of creating rules within the FRM application can be accomplished via two methods: ● Postman API - VS Code ● Try Out - Rule Builder a) Steps to create Rules via Postman API - VS Code ● Install VS Code, ● Post-Installing click on “New Text File” and select JSON as language','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 43, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
