requestParams.score_
agg
json Aggregation logic is defined here Whether
the score needs to be displayed as
cumulative of all rules triggered or max /
min score from all rules triggered
userId Integer unique id of the webuser can be put
attribs Array of fields used for determining
aspects of real time / batch processing of
transactions
attribs.type String type decide the decision is for
Realtime/Batch/Workflow
attribs.store This gives details of various sinks for
the score process - used by Async. Its an
array of fields used like name of store,
connection used to store, tables to store
values, fields returned after Insert.
attribs.store.name String name of the table
attribs.store.connec
tion
String Connection used to store values in db schema
like analytical/transactional db - this is
configured in config.json
attribs.store.tablen
ame
String Used to indicate the table to be referred
to store the values
attribs.store.fields JsonArr
ay
Details of fields to be saved in
respective columns to db for mentioned
table
attribs.store.return
ing
String field which will be returned after insert
-- to be provided if needed for subsequent
tables..Like ilivemessageid for decision
details
attribs.rule_pr Array Details of rule processing - rule
defaults, fields to return in rule
response
attribs.rule_pr.resp
osne
Array The fields to return in result response
should consist of all field required for
rules to be loaded in decision details
attribs.rule_pr.retu
rn_defaults
JSON The default values for every rule result..
These values are set if the rule does not
return them
attribs.txntype String Type of the transaction like
Transaction/Profile/Onboarding/Simulation
attribs.whitelist Array Json logic for whitelist should be
declared here.
attribs.dependents Array Data to be loaded for scoring from
DB,Redis,Mem as of now
attribs.dependents.k
ey
Array For redis a jsonarray for DB as multiple
keys can be used
key to be used from the data redis db
attribs.dependents.n
ame
String Name which will be the prefix in
dictionary for scoring line if its vpa
then payer,payee and if it''s account then
payeracc, payeeacc
attribs.dependents.t
ype
String redis, where to get the data from
attribs.dependents.o
bject
String connection from dbs like profiles
