ned below "values" object For e.g., consider the "High Value Transaction" rule, which triggers an alert whenever a transaction exceeds 50,000. In this instance, the threshold value is set at 50,000. ● "type" determines whether it should be an ALERT based or BLOCK based or BRANCH rule (Link to Rule Order) ● "fail.score" and “fail.remarks” determine the score and remarks that need to be displayed when the rule is triggered. ● "success.score" and “success.remarks” determine the score and remarks that needs to be displayed when the rule is not triggered and passed in evaluation','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 4, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
