ied in conjunction with the JOIN function, treats the merged array as a data array. ● It then proceeds to evaluate each dictionary or member within that array against a predefined set of logical checks, which are specified following the join operation. For e.g., { "if": [ { "some": [ { "join": [ { "var": "datalist" }, [ { "var": "observations"','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 30, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
