ys ● timeSince function returns milliseconds since given date-time. Syntax: { "timeSince": [ ]} ● days as a function converts the number of days specified to milliseconds. Useful in combination with timeSince. { "days": [ ] } ● Mostly we use timeSince in combination with the days function to calculate date-difference.','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 35, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
