Customers API is used to create new Customers. A Customer may have
multiple Accounts for Savings, Current, Credit, Prepaid & Loan.
The API supports CRUD operations and the details on the same are
also given below. Example JSON input message structures for
creating a Customer is given below:
> `[POST /customers]` to add a customer
> `[PUT /customers/{id}]` to update a customer
> `[PATCH /customers/{id}]` to update a specific record(s) for a customer
> `[DELETE /customers/{id}]` to soft-delete a customer
> `[GET /customers/{id}]` to fetch a customer record
1.2.1 Customers API - Example (Person)
header:"Content-Type: application/json"
