To use any of the group by, sort by, split by or where
filter, the user can just drag and drop the column headers
from the custom datagrid into any of the fields. Each filter
can be used standalone or coupled with the other filters.
The Where field requires a numeric value to be entered
accordingly, which would fit the desired condition of the
greater than, less than or equal to criteria.
