vcruleparams.wgt or vcruleparams.error.wgt
● Under store, we define tables to store the values like
ilvetrans and trans for Realtime and batchtrans for Batch
decisions
● For both tables we have to define each field, like from where
the data should be fetched(value- name from data dict
which is request and result. Request contains
observations also),what is the datatype(type) and column
name where to store the values(column)
● Adding a whitelist logic contains the name of the list - name
for refdata to be used to run this whitelist on i e
whitelist_itenantid, whitelist_logic define the condition
whitelist logic of which field ,values you are creating
a whitelist
● key in dependents contains name (db table to be referred),
val (path from where the values to be picked) and keytype
(datatype of the value received). it should be tagged along
with itenantid (refer decision json above).
● Dependents should also contain the names of the lists
tenantwise.
