Valid for Mastercard : 0,1,2
payer.addr* String Payer''s Payment Address e.g.
kalicharan@ok
Specification - Max length = 255
payer.type* String Payer’s type e.g. PERSON|ENTITY
payer.amount* Integer Transaction amount in Paise e.g. 50000
Specifications - Min digits = 1, Max
digits = 13
payer.currency* String ISO 4217 format. Also supports crypto
currencies. Examples: EUR, BTC, USDT
payer.mobilenum String Beneficiary Mobile number as per NEFT
e.g. +91.99999.99999
payer.attribs Additional Attributes for Payer (valid
attributes listed below)
