txn.attribs Additional Attributes for the transaction.
(Valid attributes listed below)
txn.attribs.skip_pro
cessing
Integer Value that determines the processing
approach for the transaction. Default
value set to 0
0 - Skip nothing
-1 - Skip rule processing,i.e risk scoring
-2 - Skip risk scoring + realtime agg
txn.attribs.key_name String One or more custom fields can be added
under txn.attribs denoted by key_name, if
required
txn.attribs.session_
id
String Session ID of Transaction e.g 001
txn.attribs.device_h
ash
String Device Hash of Transaction e.g
dc5c7986daef50c1e02ab09b442ee34f
payer.addr* String Payer''s Payment Address e.g. kalicharan@ok
Specification - Max length = 255
payer.type* String Payer’s type e.g. PERSON|ENTITY
payer.amount* Integer Transaction amount in Paise e.g. 50000
Specifications - Min digits = 1, Max
digits = 13
payer.currency* String ISO 4217 format. Also supports crypto
currencies. Examples: EUR, BTC, USDT
payer.attribs Additional Attributes for Payer (valid
attributes listed below)
payer.attribs.identi
ty.type
String Verified ID type e.g. AADHAAR
payer.attribs.identi
ty.verified_name
String Verified Name of the Payer e.g. Kalicharan
payer.attribs.identi
ty.email_id
String Email ID of the payer e.g.
kalicharan02@gmail.com
payer.attribs.device Map Details of device/terminal used by payer
for this transaction (Valid attributes
listed below)
payer.attribs.device
.id
String Terminal ID of the device as per NPCI or
ISO 20022
payer.attribs.device
.mobile num
String Mobile Number of payer e.g.
+91.99999.99999
payer.attribs.device
.geocode
String lat,long e.g. 12.9667,77.5667
payer.attribs.device
.location
String Device location e.g. Bangalore, Bangalore,
Karnataka
payer.attribs.device
.ip
String IP address of the device e.g.
123.456.123.123
payer.attribs.device
.type
String Type of the device e.g. Mobile | Computer
payer.attribs.device
.os
String OS version of the device e.g. Android
11|IOS12|Windows
payer.attribs.device
.app
String App used by the party to do this
transaction e.g. Gpay|PhonePe
payer.attribs.device
.capability
String Device Capability e.g. 11001
payee.addr* String Payee''s Payment Address e.g. amazon@upi
Specification - Max length = 255
