fractions and timezone) e.g.
2021-05-26T19:46:24.000+05:30
txn.id* String Unique identifier of the payment (Unique
& Case Sensitive) e.g. djri5fhdG4kd
Specifications - Min length = 1, Max
length = 35
txn.orgTxnId* String Original Transaction ID, if this
transaction is in relation to another
(Case Sensitive) e.g. Trxn1
txn.note String Transaction note by customer e.g. Rent
payment
txn.type* String Type of the transaction e.g.
PAY|COLLECT|DEBIT|CREDIT|REVERSAL|REFUND
|FAILED
txn.class* String Classifier indicating organization code
or payment product or payment channel
(to be mutually decided at the time of
implementation). Few examples of
transaction classes currently supported
are UPI|API, CARD|API, NEFT|ONLINE,
UPI|ONLINE, CARD|POS, CARD|ONLINE,
BNPLUPI|API, IMPS|ONLINE | PREAUTH|UPI
txn.value_date String Date on which transaction should be
settled e.g. 2021-08-30
txn.attribs Additional Attributes for the
transaction. (Valid attributes listed
below)
txn.attribs.skip_pro
cessing
Integer Value that determines the processing
approach for the transaction. Default
value set to 0
0 - Skip nothing
-1 - Skip rule processing,i.e risk
scoring
-2 - Skip risk scoring + realtime agg
txn.attribs.auth String Type of authorization e.g.
AADHAAR|OTP|MPIN
txn.attribs.benefici
ary_alert
Additional attributes for beneficiary
alerts of NEFT
txn.attribs.benefici
ary_alert.mobilenum
Mobile number to be intimated
txn.attribs.benefici
ary_alert.email
Email id to be intimated
txn.attribs.session_
id
String Session ID of Transaction e.g 001
txn.attribs.device_h
ash
String Device Hash of Transaction e.g
dc5c7986daef50c1e02ab09b442ee34f
txn.attribs.card_dat
a.product_details.it
em_id
Integer Item number in the cart e.g. 1
txn.attribs.card_dat
a.product_details.pr
oduct_code
String Product code of the product being
purchased e.g. 2000
txn.attribs.card_dat
a.product_details.pr
oduct_name
String Name of the Product being Purchased e.g.
Apple Watch
