middle_name String Middle Name of the customer eg.Mayer
last_name String Last Name of the customer eg. Doe
user.email array Array of email accounts associated
with the customer eg. [
johnm@gmail.com, jon@yahoo.com,
jdoe@xyz.com)
user.number array Array of phone numbers associated
with the customer eg. [ 9198898898,
9188998899]
