Windows allow to capture a specific set or a group transaction
under a specific time window, the specifications can be set for
the payer or payee side.
The RT window table consists of the following information:
● WIN ID: Unique window ID
● NAME: Name of the Window.
● DURATION: P1D/P2D
● REMARKS: Any remarks associated with the created window.
● STATUS: Approved/Rejected
● LAST UPDATE: Last update date and time of the window.
● ACTION: View or delete the window.
