ruledetail(rule JSON) - in strings, vcruleparams (in strings) and vcruleorder (in string) ● To convert the required in strings use JSON-String Converter ● Once CSV is prepared, visit Postman and import the Rule CSV collection. ● Click on “Upload Rules - A” POST request and verify the Body section to ensure that all variables are properly parameterized in relation to the rule CSV. Additionally, confirm that the action parameter is explicitly set to "A" indicating addition. ● Once verified, upload rule CSV to the collection and run the collection with a delay of 500ms','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 44, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
