1.5.6 Simple Customers Request - Parameters
Parameter Type Description
externalId* String Customer account ID /AgentID in external
system (Unique & Case Sensitive) e.g.
RT10736
Specifications - Min length = 3, Max length
= 100, Unique, Cannot be NULL, Cannot be
Updated
customerName* String Name of the customer e.g. PRAKASH RAGHVAN
Specifications - Min length = 1, Max length
= 200, Cannot be NULL
verifiedName String Name of the customer verified with an
approved government identity document i.e.
AADHAAR, Passport etc. e.g. John Pearson
Specifications - Min length = 1, Max length
= 200, Cannot be NULL
customerType String Customer’s type e.g. PERSON|ENTITY
Specifications - Min length = 1, Max length
= 50, Cannot be NULL
accountNumber String account number
accountType Integer Type of Account : 1. Savings, 2. Credit, 3.
Loan & 4. PrePaid
ifsc String IFSC code
payment_address* String Unique payment address of the customer if
different from the organisation’s
identifier e.g. RT10736
Specification - Max length = 255
merchant Bit Whether customer is a merchant or not e.g.
TRUE|FALSE
onboarding_date String timestamp of onboarding of the customer
e.g. 2020-01-13T12:00:00
Specifications - onboarding date time as
local ISO8601 format
i.e. `yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss`
postal_code String Postal Code of Customer e.g. 311001
Specification - Max length = 20
email String Customer’s email id e.g.
johny1979@gmail.com
Specification - Max length = 255
registered_mobile String Customer’s registered mobile number e.g.
+91 9834782422
Specification - Max length = 255
default_mcc String Default mcc assigned to customer e.g. 12.
Set to 0 by default
iso_country_code String ISO country code of customer’s residence
e.g. IN
Specification - Max length = 2
address_geolocation onboarding geolocation of the customer
