1.1.3 Standalone Payment Address API – Parameters
Parameter Type Description
externalId* String Unique External ID of payment address
for the organisation’s identifier
(Case Sensitive)e.g. R0001f12
Specifications - Min length = 3, Max
length = 100, Unique, Cannot be NULL,
Cannot be Updated
payment_address String Unique payment address of the customer
if different from the organisation’s
identifier e.g. sujoym@okhdfc
Specification - Max length = 255
vpaName String Name of the virtual payment account
e.g. Sujoy Mondal
Specification - Max length = 200
onboarding_date String Date of onboarding of the customer
e.g. 2020-01-13
Specifications - ISO-8601 Pattern =
yyyy-mm-dd, Timezone = IST
Merchant Bit Whether customer is a merchant or not
e.g. TRUE|FALSE
Verified Bit Whether customer is verified or not
e.g. TRUE|FALSE
attribs.cash_limit Integer Upper Cash limit set for withdrawal on a
card e.g. 7500000 (for person)
attribs.credit_limi
t
Integer Monthly expenditure limit for a card e.g.
8000000 (for person)
attribs.ecom Bit Whether the merchant is an e-commerce
org (for merchant)
