1.1 Background
Drona Pay helps financial institutions mitigate risk in Payments
and Lending. We support a range of products including Credit Card,
Debit Card, BNPL, UPI, NEFT,AEP5S & IMPS. The channels for the
transactions include APIs, Payment gateways, Net banking & Mobile
banking apps. We cover transactional risk scoring in real time
use cases for Banks, BNPL, Payment processors and FinTechs.
The high level implementation follows two models: Bank and FinTech
(PSP, BNPL, Wallet etc.). In the Bank implementation model the
Drona Pay Risk Scoring solution interfaces with the Switch/Gateway
(UPI, NEFT, CC, RTGS etc.). The Switch / Gateway will send payment
requests to both FRM and Core Banking/ Limit validation systems.
If both systems approve of the transaction the same will be
approved by the Switch.
Fig 1: Bank Implementation Model
In the FinTech implementation model the processing engine for the
products like payment or wallet or BNPL will interface with Drona
Pay and send messages for risk scoring.
