1.3 Accounts API
Accounts API is used to create new Accounts. A Customer may have
multiple Accounts for different offerings like Savings, Current,
Credit, PrePaid & Loan. The message structure is nested with the
ability to support opening of single or multiple Accounts for a
Customer.
The API supports CRUD operations and the details on the same are
also given below. Example JSON input message structures for
creating an Account is given below:
> `[POST customers/{id}/accounts]` to add an account for a customer
`[POST /accounts]` to add an account without linkage to customer
> `[PUT /accounts/{id}]` to update an account
