d, click on “NEXT” button and in step 3 define the required rule params. ● Click on “NEXT” button, once details of rule params are filled out ● As the final step, choose the dimension of the rule, and then select the option "Save to Rules Available." ● Once saved, verify the same under rules available section. ● Once verified, go to Menu -> Masters -> Rules -> Select the Decision (where you want to add the rule) ● Then from LHS panel i.e under “Transaction” section, SELECT the rule that you want to add to the decision','{"Date": "2025-03-24", "DocName": "Rule Doc", "Page ID": 47, "Version": 5, "iTenantID": 17}');
