1.2.2 Transaction Class - Parameters
Parameter Type Description
txnClassName* String Class name to be used as identifier of a
particular group of transactions e.g. Bank
Name | Payment Type | Customer Type
productID* Integer Internal Id associated with the Product
for which the class is being created
channelID* Integer Internal Id associated with the Payment
Channel for which the class is being
created
decisionID* Integer Internal Id associated with the Decision
mapped to rules which would be fired for
the class being created
payerMandatory* Boolean Whether payer registration is mandatory
e.g. TRUE | FALSE
payeeMandatory* Boolean Whether payee registration is mandatory
e.g. TRUE | FALSE
active* Boolean Whether the class is active i.e. currently
in use e.g. TRUE | FALSE
record_status Integer Value set to 0 for create and update.
Value set to 1 for delete.
skip_processing Integer Value that determines the processing
approach for the transaction. Default
value set to 0
- 0 - Skip nothing
-1 - Skip rule processing,i.e risk scoring
-2 - Skip risk scoring + realtime agg
