Parameter Type Description
availableRuleID Integer Default Rule ID from Rule Master - Drona
Pay that the current rule is derived from.
This ID is common across implementations
ruleID Integer Rule ID specific to the implementation.
This is a unique identifier for the rule
decisionID Integer Decision ID that the rule is mapped to
ruleName String Rule Name. This field can be common across
multiple decisions
ruleDescription String Detail regarding the rule, if any
ruleDetails String Core rule logic scripted using JSONLogic
(Stringified)
