Transaction history, OTP Success etc.
Eventtime String Timestamp of event entry (ISO-8601 with
fractions and timezone) e.g.
2021-05-26T19:46:24.000+05:30
Eventstatus String Status of the event
Eventamount String Amount involved e.g. 5000000
attribs.crm-ref String Reference ID
1.5 Account Events API
Account Events API is used to intimate the system of events
related to a specific account or a customer or a specific VPA. For
e.g. a reported fraud or settlement of bill (credit card).
Example JSON input message structure for different account events
for an account / customer / vpa is given below, where
{external_id} = external_id of the Customer/ Account or
VPA/Payment address given at the time of creating the masters.
The API supports CRUD operations and the details on the same is
also given below:
> `[POST /customers/{external_id}/events]` to add a customer event
> `[POST /accounts/{external_id}/events]` to add an account event
> `[POST /payment_addresses/{external_id}/events]` to add a VPA event
> `[DELETE /events/{id}]` to delete an account event
> `[GET /events/{id}]` to fetch an account event
1.5.1 Account Events API – Bill Paid Example
Endpoint: POST /payment_addresses/{external_id}/events
Content-Type: "1"
body:
{
"externalId": "payin-20220301-1",
"eventType": "BILLPAID",
"eventTime": "2022-03-01T10:30:50.000+05:30",
