To Create a New simulation:
24 |',17,'6a473a65-68eb-4a84-9393-0b9ee8c125d4');
INSERT INTO agents.user_manual(doc_name,version,date,pageid,page_content,itenantid,docid) VALUES ('User Manual',1,'2025-03-24',25,'● Click on the “Add New Simulation” button
● Provide the simulation with a name and a description
● Select batch or real time along with the decision and rule
that needs to be tested; and click on the “ADD” button.
4.2 Analyze Simulation
Once the simulation is run the User is redirected to the Analyze
simulation section. Here the user can preview the analysis of
previously run simulations and the ones which were recently
created.
To preview simulation results:
● Select a simulation from the simulation dropdown menu.
● Select ‘nth’ run that the simulation underwent.
● Select a date range.
All the transactions with dates and scores achieved by the
simulations under previously set and new set of thresholds are
displayed to user analysis.
The “Compare Thresholds” table displays the threshold limits set
